            </div> *@
            
            @* <div class="info-box">
                <strong>Important Note:</strong><br/>
                • This verification code is valid for 15 minutes<br/>
                • Do not share this code with anyone<br/>
                • If you did not make this request, please ignore this email
            </div> *@
            
            @* <p class="message">
                The target content of your dmca notice will be remain on our platform. If you believe this is a mistake, you may consider submitting a new DMCA notice with accurate information.
            </p>

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>Important Note:</strong><br />
